def: A genus of marine gastropods having a long, tapering spire.They belong to the Toxoglossa. Called also auger shell.
In an asexual manner; without sexual agency.
Of the same kind or nature; having the same substance oressence; coessential.Christ Jesus . . . coeternal and consubstantial with the Father andwith the Holy Ghost. Foxe.
Of or containing aluminium; as, aluminic phosphate.
A large East Indian nocturnal tree snake (Dipsas dendrophila).It is not venomous.
A sharper; a rogue. [Obs.] J. Webstar.
The act or process of being Russified.
